title: SPECIALS-$250 OFF One Months Rent
posting_body: ['For leasing info call or text', 'show contact info', 'today!', 'Ask about ID#77551', 'Enjoy the convenience of a premier Uptown address while living in a community that provides a peaceful retreat from the bustle of the city.', 'This community is ideally located in the world-famous Galleria area, home to many of the nation’s most prestigious companies, shops, restaurants and entertainment venues.', 'Experience living in your own private sanctuary from the outside world overlooking streams, ponds, scenic gardens and a five-acre wooded park.', 'Amenities', 'With its carefully designed amenities and outstanding location, this community is destined to become the ultimate living experience.', 'Phase I', '5 Acre Wooded Park', 'Scenic Gardens, Streams, Ponds', 'Pool/Spa', 'Wi-Fi in Leasing Center & poolside', '24 Hour Fitness Center', 'Direct Access Parking Garage', 'Phase II', '5 Acre Wooded Park', 'Fountain Courtyards', 'Pool/Spa', '24 Hour Fitness Center', 'Direct Access Parking Garage w/ Elevator', 'Trash Chutes', 'Located in the vibrant and exciting River oaks District/Uptown/Galleria area, this community has one of the most desirable addresses in Houston.', 'At this community you can park (free of charge) in the multi-level Parking Garage.', 'You can relax and surf the internet Poolside, in Phase I, or stay in shape at the 24 hour Fitness Center.', 'From Post Oak Park you are just minutes away from the scenic Memorial Park and all of its recreational activities including Texas’ top-rated Municipal 18 hole Golf Course, 3 Mile Running Course, as well as facilities for Tennis, Softball, Swimming, Track, Croquet, Volleyball, In-line Skating and Cycling.']
